dcpwizard (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * Full DCP creation from JPEG 2000 + audio MXF inputs
  * JPEG 2000 encoding via OpenJPEG (CPU) and Grok (GPU)
  * AES-128 content encryption with KDM generation
  * DCP verification and quality control
  * CLI and desktop GUI (Tauri 2)

